      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-driven-volatility-sends-asian-funds-searching-for-shelter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）惩罚关税萨尔沃斯（Salvos）和频繁的人字拖入对亚洲基金经理的挑战：如何避免在标题驱动的市场中进行任何潜在的擦拭。]]></description>
