    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀证明很粘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-08/inflation-is-proving-sticky-as-fed-chair-powell-heads-to-the-hill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国通货膨胀在今年年初显示出势头的迹象很少，而健康的就业增长使经济体现了，这支持了美联储的立场，以保持利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-08/inflation-is-proving-sticky-as-fed-chair-powell-heads-to-the-hill</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>即使特朗普的关税谈话也无法改变债务衍生品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-08/cds-spreads-are-so-tight-even-trump-tariff-talk-can-t-shift-them-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使是美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税言论也无法骚扰信贷市场，这向一些货币经理和战略家的标志表明，市场太沾沾自喜了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-08/cds-spreads-are-so-tight-even-trump-tariff-talk-can-t-shift-them-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 08 Feb 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
